latestIgtvVideos.title: Aksari resort, Ubud, Bali - Cinematic video
latestIgtvVideos.caption: When we were in Ubud, we stayed at this luxurious property @aksariubud managed by @iniviehospitality. This place offers you the perfect getaway, in the midst of the forest where you wake up to the sound of the birds chirping and the sun lighting up the place. We couldn’t get enough of it. Will surely come back for more. Check out the video, tell me if it doesn’t tempt you ♨️ Shot & edited @thevatsalshah_ 💕

Okay but why did no one tell me @hitchkiindia – Nesco is this fun?! 🤯
From the vibe to the food to the desserts (yes, I tried Angry Bird and it was a whole show) — everything was top tier 👌

The staff? Super sweet.
The ambience? Feels like a party, even on a random Tuesday.
Speaking of Tuesdays… Talli Tuesday is a game-changer — cocktails starting at just ₹123 😮‍💨
 
If you’re looking for a spot that’s fun, chill, and actually worth the hype — this is it. @truetalent.mgt
